```
@Bean
public AmazonS3 amazonS3() {
    InstanceProfileCredentialsProvider provider
      = new InstanceProfileCredentialsProvider(true);
    return AmazonS3ClientBuilder.standard()
      .withCredentials(provider)
      .build();
}
```

